machine_end_gcode:
{if max_layer_z < max_print_height}G1 Z{z_offset+min(max_layer_z+30, max_print_height)} F600 ; Move print bed down{endif}
G1 X210 Y210 F1000 ; present print
G91 ;Relative positioning
G1 E-3 F2700 ;Retract a bit
M140 S0 ; turn off heatbed
M104 S0 ; turn off temperature
M107 ; turn off fan
M84 X Y E ; disable motors
machine_start_gcode:
; ------------
; Custom gcode
M140 S[first_layer_bed_temperature] ;Start heating bed
M104 S170; start warming hotend to 170
M190 S[first_layer_bed_temperature] ;Wait for bed to reach temp before proceeding

G28 ;Home
;M501 ; Reload last-saved bed leveling
;M420 S1 ; restaure auto leveling mesh
BED_MESH_PROFILE LOAD=default

G92 E0 ;Reset Extruder
G1 Y+220.0 X50.0 F4000.0 ; go outside print area
M104 S[first_layer_temperature] ;Start heating extruder
M109 S[first_layer_temperature] ;Wait for extruder to reach temp before proceeding
G1 Z0.0 F300.0;
G1 X150 E15.0 F1000.0 ; intro line
G1 Y+218.0 E15.0 F1000.0 ; intro line
G1 X100 E15.0 F1000.0 ; intro line

G92 E0 ;Reset Extruder
G1 Z2.0 F3000 ;Move Z Axis up
; End custom gcode
; ------------
name: Ender5
